OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud and rain clearing
OL,6,Fto give some bright or sunny spells,
OL,7,Fbut also scattered showers. The
OL,8,Fshowers turning heavy, with risk of
OL,9,Fhail and thunder in places, especially
OL,10,Fduring the afternoon. Light winds
OL,11,Fgenerally, but locally gusty near
OL,12,Fshowers.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FFurther heavy and possibly
OL,15,Fthundery showers during the evening.
OL,16,FThe showers gradually easing after
OL,17,Fdusk to leave a largely dry night,
OL,18,Fwith clear spells developing. Breezy
OL,19,Fand staying mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
