OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA bright start, before a
OL,6,Fband of rain spreads northeastwards
OL,7,Facross all parts during the afternoon.
OL,8,FRain clearing by late-afternoon with
OL,9,Fsome scattered showers following on
OL,10,Fbehind. Temperatures near normal.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FBreezy on Thursday, with sunny spells
OL,14,Fand showers, heavy and thundery. Fewer
OL,15,Fshowers likely on Friday. Drier and
OL,16,Fbrighter on Saturday, but rain is
OL,17,Fpossible later. Staying cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
